WITH source_data AS (

    FROM DBT.dbt_rchittipolu.stg_raw_players

scd_updates AS (
    SELECT
        s.PlayerID,
        s.PlayerName,
        s.PlayerRole,
        s.BattingStyle,
        s.BowlingStyle,
        s.Nationality,
        s.updated_at,
        COALESCE(p.effective_date, current_date()) AS effective_date,
        NULL::date AS expiration_date,
